Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:11.26,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.37,0:00:15.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground with a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:23.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:27.04,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning with a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:30.77,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.77,0:00:34.47,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.47,0:00:37.89,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:45.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Tearing through the\Nair with a Rider Plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.56,0:00:53.08,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great flight that\Nskates over the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:56.84,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up tornadoes with a Rider Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.84,0:01:00.74,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.74,0:01:04.48,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.48,0:01:08.30,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.30,0:01:11.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.09,0:01:15.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.15,0:01:19.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.98,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,160.389)}The Monstrous Garaox's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.98,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx130\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,710.389)}Flying Cars!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.79,0:01:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsuhiko, this is so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.86,0:01:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the air really\Nis better outside of Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.50,0:01:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.57,0:01:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that mist?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.14,0:01:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsuhiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.78,0:02:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really thick... damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.92,0:02:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see an inch in front of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.78,0:02:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanae, close the windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.05,0:02:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,0:02:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange... we should be\Nout of the tunnel by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.53,0:02:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't even tell where\Nwe are with all this fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.02,0:02:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.27,0:02:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get out and have a look outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.01,0:02:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You stay here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.82,0:02:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.52,0:02:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.22,0:02:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're up in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold the power of the devil mist!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.56,0:02:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:03:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's falling from the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, we must get to the\Nbottom of this at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, speak to me! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.65,0:03:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A toll road...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:36.07,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50\c&H365C02&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Kamen Rider\N {\c&H000000&}Kid Corps Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Devil mist! Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't make sense of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.98,0:03:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How could a person fall from the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.31,0:03:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.22,0:03:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet he was skydiving!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a parachute?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Good point...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:03:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There were no aircraft passing\Nabove at that time, they said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So we know for sure\Nhe didn't fall out of a plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a toll road ticket he had on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dated today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean he wasn't\Nin a plane, but in a car?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how did he end up in the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.29,0:04:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, General Black?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My devil mist is fifty times more\Npowerful than hydrogen gas,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,previously thought to be the\Nlightest substance on Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A victory of Gel Shocker's science division,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,taking a hint from the dirigibles\Nof Nazi Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We will use it to send all of Earth's\Nvehicles rising into the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be enough to inspire\Npanic in the world below.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But that won't be enough\Nto satisfy Gel Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll then crash the\Nvehicles into the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If this works, then all of Japan\Nwill soon fall into our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.14,0:05:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,fusion cyborg of ox and\Nman-eating crow... Garaox!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The man in question survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:05:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.30,0:05:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is that man now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir. He was saved by the Kamen Rider,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and is now at the Rider\NKid Corps headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.91,0:06:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.82,0:06:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use my devil mist to finish off that\Nman, and the Kamen Rider with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're sure this car fell from the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. There were quite a few witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this it? The car that fell from the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.32,0:06:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Was anyone inside it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman... I'm afraid she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A license!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.07,0:07:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the man I saved earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.83,0:07:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This man was definitely in this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.09,0:07:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really have to be in such a hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.82,0:07:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you at least wait for the\NChairman and Mr. Hongo to return?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.66,0:07:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.95,0:07:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Mr. Hongo who gave the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He did? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants him conscious\Nagain as soon as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,to find out what he knows about Gel Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.98,0:07:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? Did the man wake up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They just took him to the\Nhospital in an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:07:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:07:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.86,0:08:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They said they were\Non orders from Mr. Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Contact Hongo at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.81,0:08:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Hongo Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready to go on the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.60,0:08:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo! The ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You've fallen for my trap, Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.06,0:10:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Garaox.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.96,0:10:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is where you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.38,0:10:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Pipe down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Garaox! You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold the power of my devil mist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.94,0:10:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What does this mist do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.22,0:10:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll find out soon enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.48,0:10:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The ambulance is flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.16,0:11:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Rider inside it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.57,0:11:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.40,0:11:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you impressed\Nby Garaox's devil talons?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too cramped to fight in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Garaox, let's go outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! Look out there first!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you now see what\Nthe devil mist can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... the devil mist has the\Npower to lift anything into the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll crash into the ground,\Nstill inside this ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider! You will die in that form!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:11:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.27,0:12:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:13:04.50,Bumper Episode 70-98,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\c&HE4EBE4&\pos(320,534)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's not the time to be\Ncaught up in mourning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki! How could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chairman thinks of\NMr. Hongo as his own son...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.17,0:13:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Choco. Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.99,0:13:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't consider your feelings in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker is trying\Nto throw Japan into chaos
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,by lifting vehicles into\Nthe air like hot air balloons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.69,0:13:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And with Hongo gone... they'll\Nprobably move their plan into full force.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:13:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the foggiest idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have to find it, no matter what,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and stop the attack from going forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.67,0:14:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What if...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What if Gel Shocker received\Nnews that Hongo was still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.12,0:14:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our Chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we could lure them to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Open as broad a band as you can\Nand spread the word on radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What word?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"This is Kamen Rider Kid Corps HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a patient in critical\Ncondition. Name: Hongo Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare for surgery at once."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.55,0:14:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman. We'll avenge him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.17,0:15:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll set out mines and lure them to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right.\N- Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, destroy that bullet train!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:19.69,Italics,,0,0,0,,Emergency communication!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.74,0:15:22.86,Italics,,0,0,0,,It seems Hongo Takeshi is still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.28,0:15:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:26.73,Italics,,0,0,0,,This is the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:28.82,Italics,,0,0,0,,"This is Kamen Rider Kid Corps HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:31.95,Italics,,0,0,0,,We have a patient in critical\Ncondition. Name: Hongo Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:33.83,Italics,,0,0,0,,Prepare for surgery at once."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Garaox!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Hongo Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.74,0:15:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll finish you off once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.83,0:15:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys! Help us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.91,0:15:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, a blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.25,0:15:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrap it up tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:15:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that should do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll look like Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right.\N- Let him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Mr. Hongo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.50,0:16:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo is on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,An emergency transmission\Nfrom headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you the power\Nof my talon missiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.73,0:18:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. It's all going as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You... You're Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.51,0:18:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Hongo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:18:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We knew that if you put\Nyour plan into practice,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.75,0:19:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd throw Tokyo into a mass panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.15,0:19:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We put on a little act to stop you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.55,0:19:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.36,0:19:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:19:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought you pitiful\Nweaklings could defeat me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.93,0:20:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me!\NJust hit the detonator!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.69,0:20:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops! Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,0:20:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops! Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.70,0:20:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Taki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.37,0:20:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.57,0:20:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.90,0:20:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.68,0:20:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Garaox... your evil deeds\Nwill not be forgiven!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:20:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:46.32,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:49.74,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:52.90,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:57.10,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.12,0:21:00.35,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:04.52,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.52,0:21:07.07,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:10.67,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.61,0:21:15.22,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.22,0:21:18.88,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.85,0:21:29.34,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.44,0:21:33.22,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies made of demons
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.22,0:21:36.69,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:40.27,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:43.98,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.98,0:21:47.88,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my scarf of red...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.88,0:21:50.78,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.32,0:21:53.82,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.82,0:21:58.30,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.30,0:22:01.55,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.37,0:22:12.70,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.04,0:22:16.06,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies spreading fear
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.54,0:22:20.20,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten our towns,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Garaox... you've picked\Nthe wrong setting to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.36,0:21:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.04,0:21:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only use your\Ndemon mist in tight spaces!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.30,0:21:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.95,0:21:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have one more power\Nto show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Gore!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.86,0:22:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Lunar Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.91,0:22:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.02,0:22:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.64,0:22:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops! I'm sorry to worry you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot... if you're gonna\Ndie, at least call first.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.25,0:22:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, I'm not sure that's possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.00,0:22:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what do I care?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.20,0:22:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.42,0:23:00.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Garaox tried to use his terrifying\Ndevil mist to throw Japan into chaos,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.73,0:23:02.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but Kamen Rider defeated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.71,0:23:06.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Still, Gel Shocker's\Nambitions weren't foiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.07,0:23:07.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Fight on, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:10.59,Cont,,0,70,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:13.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(280.175,262.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.53,0:23:14.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next episode will feature\Nthe monstrous Cactusbat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.26,0:23:19.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Those hit with his poison needles\Nturn into cactuses immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.26,0:23:22.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker wants to turn\Nall humans into cacti...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.97,0:23:25.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Including Hongo Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.14,0:23:30.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for "Hongo\NTakeshi Becomes a Cactus Monster!?"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.90,0:23:30.86,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx130\fs115\bord0.8\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,722.389)}Hongo Takeshi Becomes \Na Cactus Monster!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.93,0:23:39.28,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,The wind gusts across the wasteland
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.28,0:23:42.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider traverses it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.65,0:23:46.53,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Alone, all alone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.53,0:23:49.72,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Holding back my sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.72,0:23:53.63,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,I fight, I fight alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.63,0:24:00.97,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Despite my solitude,\NI will do what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.97,0:24:06.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,to protect my friends and my home
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.02,0:24:12.17,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,I am the Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The Monstrous Garaox's\NFlying Cars!!